Parameters

tgi TGI

DBPFTGI object representing the entry

offset uint

Offset (location) of the entry within the DBPF file

size uint

Compressed size of data for the entry, in bytes. Uncompressed size is also temporarily set to this to this until the data is set

index uint

Entry position in the file, 0-n

bytes byte[]

Byte data for this entry
